casebody.data:
No. 09-10505. Nina Shahin, Petitioner v. Delaware Department of Finance. 561 U.S. 1004, 130 S. Ct. 3493,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1054,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5062. June 21, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner is allowed until July 12, 2010, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
